  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<em>Your barrage of unarmed attacks builds to a single, staggering strike.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Medusa's Wrath.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>You may forgo the two additional unarmed strikes of Medusa's Wrath to instead make a single unarmed strike at your highest base attack bonus. If you successfully hit your opponent, it must succeed at a Fortitude saving throw (DC 10 + 1/2 your character level + your Wisdom modifier) or be staggered for 1 round. You can expend one use of mythic power when you stagger a target with Medusa's Wrath to extend the duration of the staggered condition by a number of rounds equal to half your tier.",
